<p style="margin: 0 0 16px;">Hi <%= @user.name %>,</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 16px;">Welcome to <strong>CouncilTracker</strong> — your window into Jersey City Council activity.</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 16px;">With CouncilTracker you can:</p>

<ul style="margin: 0 0 16px; padding-left: 20px;">
  <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Browse meeting agendas and track how council members vote</li>
  <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Star meetings, agenda items, and topics for quick access</li>
  <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Search across all council activity by keyword or topic</li>
</ul>

<p style="margin: 0 0 24px;">
  <a href="<%= dashboard_url %>" style="display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #2563eb; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px;">Go to Dashboard</a>
</p>

<p style="margin: 0; color: #6b7280; font-size: 13px;">Thank you for being part of civic transparency in Jersey City.</p>
